    <description><![CDATA[<h2>DataReactor(数据响应框架）</h2>

<h3>基本思想</h3>

<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;数据响应框架的基本思想是控件可以响应数据的变化，控件可以根据数据的变化做相应的处理。</p>

<h3>事件类型</h3>

<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 控件可以监听数据变化事件有：加载、更新、增加、删除、选择和全不选等。</p>

<h3>如何数据响应器</h3>

<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 要使用数据响应器，一般需要指定数据的流向，比如：button &gt; text，就是button控件的数据变化流向text控件。</p>]]></description>&#xd;
    <en_description><![CDATA[<h2>DataReactor (data response framework)</h2>

<h3>Basic idea</h3>

<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;The basic idea of the data response framework is that the control can respond to the change of data, and the control can do corresponding processing according to the change of the data. </p>

<h3>Event type</h3>

<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; The control can monitor data change events: load, update, add, delete, select, and deselect all. </p>

<h3>How to data responder</h3>

<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; To use a data responder, you generally need to specify the flow of data, such as: button &gt; text, which means that the data changes of the button control flow to the text control. </p>]]></en_description>&#xd;
</QuickContent>